A_601 - Stiletto heels are just an insult to women. They are uncomfortable and dangerous, and are an indication of the fact that there are psychological and social problems that have led women to have to make an effort just to appear taller. It is difficult for a woman to be completely friendly by wearing shoes like that, because in any case by wearing uncomfortable and dangerous shoes the first step in the wrong direction in terms of human relationships has already been taken. At most they can be thought of as shoes for doing a certain type of gymnastics, but they are still a bit dangerous.